===Check with Clara on how the robot is doing===
{{Mission Description|type=companion|location=Robot Settlement|update|You receive Clara's new message. She seems to have finished repairing the little robot.<br />Maybe you can see how things are going at Svarog's Base when you have the time. Remember, you promised her to go &mdash;<br />No one can break a promise to Clara. No one.}}
{{Dialogue Start}}
